import Card from './card'
import * as Icon from "react-bootstrap-icons";
import './main-action-buttons.css'
function MainActionButtons(props){
    return(
        <Card className="actionButtons">
          <button type="button"  className="btn btn-outline-light btn-lg">
          <Icon.ShieldPlus /> |         Create a new LAD Specification 
          </button>
          <button type="button" className="btn btn-outline-light btn-lg">
           Open and edit an existing LAD specification <Icon.LayoutWtf />
          </button>
          <button type="button" className="btn btn-outline-light btn-lg">
           Explorer and manage the current Library <Icon.Collection />
          </button>
          <button type="button" className="btn btn-outline-light btn-lg">
           Specify and manage the creation rules <Icon.GearWideConnected />
          </button>
        </Card>
    )
}

export default MainActionButtons;
